<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You elected to pay for your business insurance policy&nbsp;<b><i>[policy number]</i></b>&nbsp;through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>As recent payments have not been made, in our latest communications with you,&nbsp;<b>you decided to enter the shortfall process</b>&nbsp;with our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Close Brothers will be in touch with you directly about this process and the retrieval of the outstanding funds. However,<b>&nbsp;if you wish to contact them directly or make a payment, please call them directly on 0333 321 8566</b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Please rest assured that because of this step,&nbsp;<b>your policy remains in place and your cover is still valid</b>. However, if you have any queries in relation to your policy, please feel free to give us a call on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>